# Mini WhatsApp Chat App

## 🚀 Features
- View all chats
- Create new chats
- MongoDB integration
- Error handling (try-catch, wrapAsync)

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- EJS

## 📚 Concepts Covered
- REST Routes
- MVC Structure
- Async Error Handling
- Custom Middleware

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   npm install

2. Start server:
   node index.js

3. Open browser:
   http://localhost:8080/chats